track_notes:
Classific E Easy . Good path til Colle dei Morti at 2480 m Mt Aver : GO at left good steep path in the first part, after lok for the better way to the top. There are 2 peaks both with cross : the true peak higher and referenced is at North . 
more photo and details on :
http://www.sotaitalia.it/files/aver.pdf
track_title: class E  in summer when road to Col Lombarda is open

track_notes: Monte Aver is a nice and easy summit, you just need to be fit enought, in summer take some water. the walk is not long, and if you can you will go to Monte della Valletta
This is the second summit, it is easy, even if the sloop is hard from the Col dei Morti, it is short; another place with nice panorama and good for radio activity
